<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title || 'PanelDX — Serviço desativado' %></title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #1e293b;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --accent: #475569;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: var(--ink);
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .maintenance-card {
            width: min(520px, 100%);
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--accent);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 36px 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            margin: 0 auto 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 1.55rem;
            color: var(--ink);
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .subtitle {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.65;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }

        .status-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #334155;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .brand {
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="maintenance-card" role="main" aria-labelledby="maintenance-title">
        <div class="maintenance-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fas fa-power-off"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="status-pill">
            <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
            Serviço desativado
        </div>

        <h1 id="maintenance-title">PanelDX desativado</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            Este serviço não está mais disponível. O ambiente PanelDX foi desativado
            e não recebe novos acessos.
        </p>

        <div class="brand">PanelDX · LeAction</div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
